Items.r: 但現在他們拿到了老神醫手中的書頁，要是小櫻被他們捉回去取血試藥，三生三死飲隨時都會完成…！

Items.mt: But now that they have the page in the old doctor's hand, if Sakura is caught by them to take blood to test the medicine, the Three Lives and Three Deaths Drink will be completed any time...!
